{"tid":1281790,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[聲明]  香港連登並沒有作出任何「騎刧」某專頁之行動","createTime":"2019-07-03T11:22:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-03T14:20:42.000Z","uid":177213,"like":66,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"d2cecc02a7a317474c5855d4840a7550e236b428","tid":1281790,"uid":177213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T11:22:26.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">作為連登討論區會員之一，本人謹代表香港連登討論區一眾會員發出聲明。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n連登討論區並沒有任何「騎劫」其他與大部分會員政見不同的專頁之行動。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同時，香港連登討論區絕對保留一切權利追究不實指控。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">至於<span style=\"color: red;\">疑似「騎劫」專頁或以往呼籲群眾參與違法行動之行為</span>，經一眾會員所研究及商討後，<span style=\"color: red;\">該行動有可能由其他討論區所作出。</span><br />\n</span><br />\n（<span style=\"font-size: small;\">可參考此貼文：<br />\n<br />\n作為babycondom一員 我有事同你班連登仔講<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1277294\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1277294</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區）</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">以下列舉數個香港主要大型討論區名單</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">（註：本聲明並非指控疑似「騎劫」行動由以下討論區發出）</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">1.親子王國 , Baby-kingdom<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.baby-kingdom.com/forum.php\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.baby-kingdom.com%2Fforum.php&d=Cxq6fU51OcuVLB8gp8NaVyEyVFbloTKGHdwbQdNTMZo%3D&h=a7f53320\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.baby-kingdom.com/forum.php</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2.香港討論區 <br />\n<a href=\"https://m.discuss.com.hk/index.php?_=\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.discuss.com.hk%2Findex.php%3F_%3D&d=Cxq6fU51OcuVLB8gp8NaVyEyVFbloTKGHdwbQdNTMZo%3D&h=f1354f82\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.discuss.com.hk/index.php?_=</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n3.Uwants 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.uwants.com/index.php\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.uwants.com%2Findex.php&d=Cxq6fU51OcuVLB8gp8NaVyEyVFbloTKGHdwbQdNTMZo%3D&h=326a15a1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.uwants.com/index.php</a></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">同時，我們亦呼籲各位網民、香港市民必須小心使用網絡。各位亦須注意不同專頁、貼文之可信性。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pEsQ7MC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpEsQ7MC.png&h=8aeac4c4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我方再出作出嚴正聲明，香港連登討論區作為本港一眾大型討論區的一份子，絕對支持香港政治多元化，並且包容不同的政治聲音。</span><br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">（註：此聲明並非由香港連登討論區官方或任何機構所發出，謹屬個人之意見，並不具任何法律效用）</span>"},{"pid":"a6012d1ecc7bbbc970f0c42071478f8811511643","tid":1281790,"uid":177213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T11:22:36.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"dfd7ec8803d8ad2d4a3b0f335957bf3f3c28ca4c","tid":1281790,"uid":177213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T11:25:41.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"d117fb691a520b7f25b1630bbd574c21d85d4a09","tid":1281790,"uid":177213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T11:25:51.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"b770dcfc8fa49130360c6faf5430ffd72cbed577","tid":1281790,"uid":177213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T11:26:07.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"35a7bc30d756af68eb9a26d34d0bab5b4e5fc92f","tid":1281790,"uid":54250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T11:28:35.000Z","msg":"咪亂咁瀨地論壇名啦<br />\n想分化咩 人地都有出一分力<br />\n大家都自己人"},{"pid":"fac1baf2dca5b1eceb77dbc3183cf3e28ab1a1b2","tid":1281790,"uid":128522,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T11:31:42.000Z","msg":"淨係指出唔關連登事味算<br />\n點知隔離壇搞緊乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd445e2cd90826d3f13fe90bf695e73bd7e09107","tid":1281790,"uid":8441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T11:33:29.000Z","msg":"樓主督灰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ca6c4533193f7a799359af7bb7fcefb8f7a456b","tid":1281790,"uid":52621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T12:12:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0670d53681560f38814567a701d427b57738cc4d","tid":1281790,"uid":249242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T12:52:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f91e28859d16b50530070a581c21c7bdbdedd5a3","tid":1281790,"uid":84040,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T14:20:42.000Z","msg":"支持樓主<br />\n連登不嬲都係愛國愛黨愛警大本營<br />\n黃屍快滾回uwants香討baby kingdom<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}